issues.description: The Stock.findStockIngredient method signature in the template takes two parameters (String name, boolean caseSensitive), but the problem statement (and the solution) specify a single-parameter method findStockIngredient(String): StockIngredient. This mismatch will cause compile errors when students call findStockIngredient(name) as described and will confuse them about which signature to implement.
